snippet.title: Fallout 76: Gleaming Depths
snippet.description:
The newest update for Fallout 76 launches today! Gleaming Depths includes a ton of exciting new content, including a new raid, C.A.M.P. pets. Get all the information you need to know about the Gleaming Depths here. 

Follow us on the following sites and social media: 
Official Site – https://bethesda.net/
Facebook – https://www.facebook.com/BethesdaSoftworks.eu/
Twitter – https://twitter.com/Bethesda_UK
Instagram – https://www.instagram.com/bethesda_uk/
Threads - https://www.threads.net/@bethesda_uk
  
PEGI 18 Rating. Mature with Blood and Gore, Drug Reference, Intense Violence, Strong Language, and Use of Alcohol.
